                    <span>I went to the bookstore looking for interior deisgn books but I ended up with this book instead. It is much more than how to create space you feel comfortable in -- it is helpful ideas about how to create a home in whatever space you live in. The book also includes advice on how to enjoy everyday tasks -- like cleaning, etc. What a breath a fresh air. I didn't need any interior design books after reading this book. I create my own ideas.<P>Ann Marie M. Andrews<BR>West Harrison, NY</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Best book I Have ever read</div>
